<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='368000' id='t-368000'>if you're on the average wage in Britain today?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='370000' id='t-370000'>And the answer is about half a second.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='373000' id='t-373000'>Back in 1950,</span>
