<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='377000' id='t-377000'>to acquire that much light.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='379000' id='t-379000'>And that's seven and a half seconds of prosperity that you've gained</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='382000' id='t-382000'>since 1950, as it were,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='384000' id='t-384000'>because that's seven and a half seconds in which you can do something else,</span>
