<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='397000' id='t-397000'>you'd have had to work six hours</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='399000' id='t-399000'>to earn a candle that could burn for an hour.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='402000' id='t-402000'>In other words, the average person on the average wage</span>
