<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='426000' id='t-426000'>Tens? Hundreds? Thousands?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='428000' id='t-428000'>You know, I think it's probably millions.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='430000' id='t-430000'>Because you've got to include the man who grew the coffee,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='432000' id='t-432000'>which was brewed for the man who was on the oil rig,</span>
