<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='442000' id='t-442000'>And that's the way society works.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='445000' id='t-445000'>That's what we've achieved as a species.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:40
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='449000' id='t-449000'>In the old days, if you were rich,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='451000' id='t-451000'>you literally had people working for you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='453000' id='t-453000'>That's how you got to be rich; you employed them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='455000' id='t-455000'>Louis XIV had a lot of people working for him.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='457000' id='t-457000'>They made his silly outfits, like this,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='459000' id='t-459000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='461000' id='t-461000'>and they did his silly hairstyles, or whatever.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='464000' id='t-464000'>He had 498 people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='466000' id='t-466000'>to prepare his dinner every night.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='468000' id='t-468000'>But a modern tourist going around the palace of Versailles</span>
