<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='473000' id='t-473000'>he has 498 people doing his dinner tonight too.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='475000' id='t-475000'>They're in bistros and cafes and restaurants</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='477000' id='t-477000'>and shops all over Paris,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='479000' id='t-479000'>and they're all ready to serve you at an hour's notice with an excellent meal</span>
