<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='505000' id='t-505000'>There's no working for each other across the colonies.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='507000' id='t-507000'>And the reason for that is because there's a reproductive division of labor.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='510000' id='t-510000'>That is to say, they specialize with respect to reproduction.</span>
